How to use this python script:
  for blocking a ip use this command:
    python3 block_ip.py -ipb ipadress
  for unblocking a ip use this command:
    python3 block_ip.py -ipub ipadress
  for view the list of blocked ips use this command:
    python3 block_ip.py -iplb

If you dont have good permission to modify iptables, you need to add sudo behind the command.

